lead_paragraph: New York Mets third baseman David Wright will be out at least six weeks and perhaps a lot longer with a herniated disk in his neck, and the team didn't try to minimize the loss Friday.

headline.print_headline: Mets 3B Wright Out at Least 6 Weeks With Neck Injury
